2
00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:09.336
Author of the best-selling
novel. <i>Descent.</i>

3
00:00:09.409 --> 00:00:13.005
soon to be made into a major
motion picture. Noah Solloway.

4
00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:15.982
People know my movies.
and they see me as this. um.

5
00:00:16.049 --> 00:00:19.247
you know. this action hero. this
sort of modern-day James Bond.

6
00:00:19.319 --> 00:00:22.016
But that's all an act. of course.
I mean. that's not who I am.

7
00:00:22.489 --> 00:00:24.458
But this book. this is me.

8
00:00:24.525 --> 00:00:26.994
So what's your plan
to make money?

9
00:00:27.561 --> 00:00:28.620
Ugh. I don't know.

10
00:00:28.695 --> 00:00:30.960
His visa's about to expire.
so no one will hire him.

11
00:00:31.932 --> 00:00:34.231
I just wanted to say I
think it's so awesome

12
00:00:34.301 --> 00:00:35.581
that you're my dad's girlfriend.

13
00:00:37.304 --> 00:00:41.400
- Can I trouble you for another drink?
- Of course. Coming right up.

14
00:00:41.475 --> 00:00:43.486
There's something wrong with
him. He's losing his memory.

15
00:00:43.510 --> 00:00:46.070
He thinks I'm still married to
Helen; he thinks I own this place.

16
00:00:46.113 --> 00:00:47.843
I need to leave.

17
00:00:50.684 --> 00:00:51.845
Come in.

18
00:00:53.287 --> 00:00:54.983
Vik. this is your son.

19
00:00:55.155 --> 00:00:56.282
This is Eddie.

20
00:00:58.859 --> 00:01:01.260
- Are you with the studio?
- No.

21
00:01:01.328 --> 00:01:03.661
- So you're...
- Helen.

22
00:01:03.730 --> 00:01:05.995
I lost my partner
a few months ago.

23
00:01:06.066 --> 00:01:07.659
Oh. my God.

24
00:01:07.968 --> 00:01:10.699
Just breathe. I
lost someone. too.

25
00:01:10.771 --> 00:01:12.740
- Where are you gonna stay?
- Dad's place.

26
00:01:13.307 --> 00:01:14.741
<i>Is that a good idea?</i>

