Come on. Helen.

958
00:51:09.700 --> 00:51:11.862
Helen. come on!

959
00:51:12.870 --> 00:51:14.429
Helen!

960
00:51:24.982 --> 00:51:25.982
<i>Hello?</i>

961
00:51:26.183 --> 00:51:27.183
Hi.

962
00:51:29.853 --> 00:51:30.718
Are you mad?

963
00:51:30.788 --> 00:51:34.316
<i>No. not mad. Um. just confused.</i>

964
00:51:34.758 --> 00:51:37.626
<i>I told you the worst thing
that ever happened to me.</i>

965
00:51:37.695 --> 00:51:40.688
<i>and you just...
well. disappeared.</i>

966
00:51:40.764 --> 00:51:41.959
I know. I'm sorry.

967
00:51:44.134 --> 00:51:47.070
I'm really sorry. Do you
want to keep talking?

968
00:51:47.404 --> 00:51:49.168
<i>No. not really.</i>

969
00:51:51.709 --> 00:51:53.871
Do you want to
do something else?

970
00:52:00.951 --> 00:52:02.283
- Shh.
- What?

971
00:52:02.353 --> 00:52:04.015
- Shh. quiet.
- Why?

972
00:52:04.088 --> 00:52:05.954
Because I have a
house full of people.

973
00:52:07.758 --> 00:52:09.420
- Who's here?
- Um...

974
00:52:10.594 --> 00:52:12.392
- my daughter.
- Mm-hm.

975
00:52:12.696 --> 00:52:13.696
My son.

976
00:52:15.933 --> 00:52:17.663
His boyfriend.

977
00:52:18.802 --> 00:52:20.600
Uh. my mother.

978
00:52:20.904 --> 00:52:21.963
You got the whole family.

979
00:52:22.039 --> 00:52:23.564
And my neighbor.

980
00:52:23.641 --> 00:52:25.269
Shh. And her baby.

981
00:52:29.146 --> 00:52:30.375
It's okay.

982
00:52:43.127 --> 00:52:44.127
Mm.

983
00:52:45.329 --> 00:52:46.729
- Helen.
- Hmm?

984
00:52:46.964 --> 00:52:49.957
Design my house.

985
00:52:50.701 --> 00:52:52.067
Give me a lamp.

986
00:52:53.237 --> 00:52:55.172
Just one room. please.

987
00:52:56.874 --> 00:52:58.069
Just one room.

988
00:52:58.342 --> 00:53:00.311
Just one tiny. little room.

989
00:53:00.978 --> 00:53:02.844
Helen. just give me a rug.

990
00:53:03.881 --> 00:53:05.873
Can you give me a rug. please?

991
00:53:06.016 --> 00:53:07.040
Give me a rug.

992
00:53:07.117 --> 00:53:08.117
Can you give me a...

993
00:53:17.327 --> 00:53:18.989
- Good morning.
- Morning.

994
00:53:19.063 --> 00:53:20.929
- Coffee?
- Sure.

995
00:53:21.365 --> 00:53:22.492
How'd you sleep?

996
00:53:23.634 --> 00:53:25.102
Really well. thanks.

997
00:53:26.403 --> 00:53:28.804
I think I can get
the kids enrolled

998
00:53:28.872 --> 00:53:31.364
in the Bridgehampton high
school for the spring semester.

999
00:53:31.442 --> 00:53:33.453
so if you put this house
on the market next month...

1000
00:53:33.477 --> 00:53:35.105
Mom. I'm not moving back.

1001
00:53:35.446 --> 00:53:36.446
What?

1002
00:53:38.248 --> 00:53:39.614
I have a life here.

1003
00:53:40.117 --> 00:53:41.797
I'll help you and Dad
out as much as I can.

1004
00:53:41.852 --> 00:53:43.650
but I-I'm not moving home.

1005
00:53:44.588 --> 00:53:46.056
What am I supposed to do?

1006
00:53:47.691 --> 00:53:48.784
You will figure it out.

1007
00:53:49.727 --> 00:53:51.093
What's gotten into you?

1008
00:53:51.628 --> 00:53:52.755
Good morning.

1009
00:53:58.068 --> 00:53:59.297
- Hey.
- Hi.

1010
00:54:00.504 --> 00:54:02.097
You must be Margaret. I'm Sasha.

1011
00:54:02.439 --> 00:54:04.431
- Pleasure to meet you.

1012
00:54:05.008 --> 00:54:07.842
I'd actually love a cup of
coffee. if it's not too much trouble.

1013
00:54:11.081 --> 00:54:12.081
Thank you.

1014
00:54:31.435 --> 00:54:36.430
<i>♪ Like double cherry
pie Yeah. there she was ♪</i>

1015
00:54:37.374 --> 00:54:40.606
<i>♪ Like disco superfly ♪</i>

1016
00:54:41.845 --> 00:54:46.840
<i>♪ I smell sex and candy here ♪</i>

1017
00:54:48.252 --> 00:54:52.849
<i>♪ Who's that
lounging in my chair? ♪</i>

1018
00:54:54.291 --> 00:54:56.260
<i>- ♪ Who's that... ♪</i>
- Those your kids?

1019
00:54:57.795 --> 00:54:58.819
No.

1020
00:55:00.130 --> 00:55:02.250
Do I look like the kind of
person who would have kids?

1021
00:55:02.699 --> 00:55:04.964
- It isn't a crime.
- It should be.

1022
00:55:05.035 --> 00:55:08.631
<i>♪ Yeah. mama. this
surely is a dream... ♪</i>

1023
00:55:08.705 --> 00:55:09.705
No. they're just...

1024
00:55:10.507 --> 00:55:12.703
some refugee kids
that I met in Senegal.

1025
00:55:13.477 --> 00:55:15.708
Oh. yeah? What were
you doing out there?

1026
00:55:15.979 --> 00:55:17.208
I'm a coastal engineer.

1027
00:55:18.582 --> 00:55:19.641
How's that going?

1028
00:55:20.117 --> 00:55:21.117
Not well.

1029
00:55:21.618 --> 00:55:24.554
<i>♪ And I had too much caffeine ♪</i>

1030
00:55:24.621 --> 00:55:27.853
<i>♪ And I was thinkin'
'bout myself... ♪</i>

1031
00:55:28.926 --> 00:55:31.166
- Have a good one.
- Thanks for the tip. Jim.

1032
00:55:37.201 --> 00:55:39.295
- Can I ask you a question?
- Shoot.

1033
00:55:39.903 --> 00:55:43.237
What's with the electricity out
here? Is the grid completely off?

1034
00:55:43.941 --> 00:55:45.773
No. Just ever since
the last hurricane.

1035
00:55:45.843 --> 00:55:47.523
they only turn it on
between 9:00 and 5:00.

1036
00:55:47.611 --> 00:55:49.409
We got our own
battery bank. though.

1037
00:55:49.880 --> 00:55:51.610
This place used
to be so beautiful.

1038
00:55:51.815 --> 00:55:54.751
Yeah. well. there aren't enough
of us out here to matter anymore.

1039
00:55:54.818 --> 00:55:58.084
We can't afford those wind turbines
they got out in East Hampton. so...

1040
00:55:58.455 --> 00:55:59.455
Right.

1041
00:56:06.029 --> 00:56:07.229
<i>You here for work?</i>

1042
00:56:09.132 --> 00:56:11.533
- I am.
- Oh.

1043
00:56:13.670 --> 00:56:14.865
How much do I owe you?

1044
00:56:16.306 --> 00:56:17.569
It's on the house.

1045
00:56:19.710 --> 00:56:21.872
I haven't seen a face like
yours out here in a while.

1046
00:56:24.081 --> 00:56:25.081
I like it.

1047
00:56:30.721 --> 00:56:32.189
Yeah.

1048
00:56:38.662 --> 00:56:40.153
- Tighter.
- What?

1049
00:56:41.531 --> 00:56:43.625
Better?

1050
00:56:43.700 --> 00:56:45.692
What?

1051
00:56:47.804 --> 00:56:48.863
What's up?

1052
00:56:49.907 --> 00:56:52.103
- It's not working for me.
- What the fuck do you want?

1053
00:56:57.714 --> 00:56:59.706
You are one sick bitch.

1054
00:57:27.311 --> 00:57:28.311
<i>Stop.</i>

1055
00:57:32.849 --> 00:57:34.977
Oh. yeah.

